{"tid":301463,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己根本唔適合拍拖？","createTime":"2017-06-28T16:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T16:18:13.000Z","uid":9532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec9b443ec298048127a70282fc0bd71a15fe818","tid":301463,"uid":9532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"拍過三次拖 次次都當人地係寶 人地就當自己係草<br />\n自問都對佢地唔差 寧願甩friend底 推走正經野 都抽時間陪佢<br />\n我唔知其他女仔係咪 我就行街睇戲食飯AA制 有時仲要請埋佢<br />\n生日 大時大節 我都冇話要求送咩比我 但佢就真係可以一句生日快樂都冇 死左去陪friend冇理過我<br />\n日日都要睇佢心情 永遠我就係罪人 打我鬧我當食生菜啦<br />\n眼見自己身邊好多港女friend同男朋友日日都好sweet<br />\n其實我都好愛佢 但真係越拍越灰 我差啲因為咁有抑鬱 每次想走佢又唔比我走 我又衰心軟同自己講比多次機會佢<br />\n究竟問題係咪係我身上？係咪我條命生得唔好？係咪我做錯左啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申 好驚佢睇到呢個post又會鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5571f5bd84a6154fda38532657d9280dbde848b","tid":301463,"uid":12221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"你既問題咪就係衰心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你自己都講左<br />\n佢有唔啱 但有啲野冇得怨<br />\n佢願打 你願唔願捱？"},{"pid":"f06ef21ca8959052a9043ddcdc911944087a2b0f","tid":301463,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"AA制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e47cc96be04d080b1f1dd9496073575e5bfa33","tid":301463,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"你係咪拍緊拖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcb2b294ae8454adf7b0d40a7a11931aec7c5c9","tid":301463,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"識埋啲mk仔？"},{"pid":"7dc358ebfda8fa4e75e31188152e66b18ad32db5","tid":301463,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"你追人?"},{"pid":"feac3996b0751c00454f190bb4dfaae75076